Hi Ron,

I appreciate the warm greeting and the links.  I am somewhat familiar
with all of those products but I would rather try and build one
myself.  I&#39;m an EE and it&#39;s kind of a pride thing.  Plus, I can
explain the data better if I&#39;m using a device I actually understand
and can poke and prod as needed.  So, I&#39;d kind of like to have a
decent understanding of the equipment before I start to collect
samples.  I will look into the EVP software.  I was going to use
Audacity and some MATLAB tools we use on a regular basis, but that
might be faster.  I&#39;ll try to answer any questions you might have
regarding signal processing or electromagnetic communications phenomena.

Anyway, thanks again for the introduction.  I look forward to seeing
all of your work.  

Regards,

Anna



